NAME
    lmytfy -- let me ygor that for you

SYNOPSIS
    lmytfy-irc
    lmytfy-mattermost

DESCRIPTION
    IRC and Mattermost bot which translates some irc chatter into specific
    ygor commands (e.g. typos, shortcuts, etc.).
    
    This is written in C as a joke, if you want to contribute, there are
    rules:
      1. the hackier the better, shortest path to victory
      2. no dependencies, just import BSD/MIT/ISC files
      3. and because we're not animals:
         http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi/OpenBSD-current/man9/style.9

INSTALL
    $ ./configure
    $ make
    $ sudo make install

WHAT IS YGOR
    https://github.com/truveris/ygor
